protected_spaces_details.description: Provision for children and young people

description: Approval of Reserved Matters relating to appearance, landscaping, layout and scale pursuant to condition 1 of application number C2008/59828/OUT dated 18 May 2010 for a  residential development of 186 dwellings comprising 1 studio apartment, 26 one bedroomed and 44 two bedroomed self contained flats, 22 two bedroomed, 59  three bedroomed, 27 four bedroomed and 7 five  bedroomed houses in a mix of two storey, two storey with roof accommodation and three storey buildings (incorporating the conversion of Oak and Mayfield Houses into eight self contained dwellings), provision of a Class A1 retail premises together with a total of 321 parking spaces/garages, cycle and refuse storage, children's play areas and associated landscaping.
